content: 10 Democrats have qualified for the Houston debate on Sept 12. To take the stage, Democrats had to gain contributions from at least 130,000 donors from at least 20 states and have 2% or more support in four national or early state polls.

Joe Biden, Bernie Sanders, Pete Buttigieg, Julian Castro, Elizabeth Warren, Beto ORourke, Kamala Harris, Andrew Yang, Cory Booker, Amy Klobuchar have met all the necessary requirements to take part in the upcoming debate, which will be hosted by ABC.
